metadata.name: The Full Moons #1
metadata.description: The Full Moons (TFMs) come with joyful moon characters, hand drawn traits and stories of an Astro Child on the Moon. TFMs are unique 7777 NFTs reflecting the feelings and dreams of a refugee girl, who had to escape from her land at the age of 12. The NFT collection intends to increase the awareness for the world events, and establish a thriving community supporting refugee children. Created and illustrated by a teenager refugee artist Belinay (@belinarts).
